        <productionVolumeComment xml:lang="en">Calculated based on literature value and estimates. The production of liquid sulphur dioxide in USA in 2004 was 2.429E+8kg (U.S. International Trade Comission, Liquid Sulfur Dioxide From Canada report, December 2005). This value is scaled using GDP/PPP (USA=1.26E+13/GLO=5.65E+13) (International Monetary Fund, 2005). It is estimated, that 50% of the production volume is produced via this technology.</productionVolumeComment>
